00:16:06.333 --> 00:16:09.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[müzik yavaşça biter]

196
00:16:15.000 --> 00:16:17.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[çarpışma sesi gelir]

197
00:16:17.750 --> 00:16:18.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ne oluyor ya?

198
00:16:18.666 --> 00:16:21.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[alarm sesi gelir]

199
00:16:27.375 --> 00:16:29.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Akın! Baş torpidoda
bir sorun mu var? Ne oluyor?

200
